flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Receive failing<br/>test suite"]
    B --> C[Inspect codebase<br/>structure]
    C --> D[Read skeleton<br/>functions]
    D --> E[LLM analyzes<br/>action history]
    E --> F[Select next action]
    F --> G{Action type?}
    G -->|Inspect| H[List/inspect files]
    G -->|Read| I[Read file contents]
    G -->|Patch| J[Write code patch]
    G -->|Run tests| K[Execute test suite]
    H --> E
    I --> E
    J --> E
    K --> L{All tests pass?}
    L -->|No| M{Max iterations<br/>reached?}
    M -->|No| E
    M -->|Yes| N["Report failure:<br/>incomplete implementation"]
    L -->|Yes| O["Report success:<br/>all tests passing"]
    N --> P([End])
    O --> P